snippet.title: Persona 3 Reload: Expansion Pass | Xbox Game Pass Ultimate, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows PC
snippet.description:
She once made a choice to live. Now, she’ll need to find the answer.

The final chapter of Persona 3 Reload, Episode Aigis -The Answer-, arrives in September 2024!

Purchase the Expansion Pass on March 12th to unlock the first wave of DLC.

https://atlus.link/P3R
